The paper deals with optimization of wireless networks, specifically small-cell networks with multiple-input-single-output broadcasting (MISO-BC) backhauls. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also deals with power control, which is a key aspect of control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions simulation results, which suggests that it may fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or computer communications (cs.COM) categories.
